    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/f0429454a683054fc8f6b010afcbf884.poster.avif?t=1641250627\" width=650 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/f0429454a683054fc8f6b010afcbf884.webm?t=1641250627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/f0429454a683054fc8f6b010afcbf884.mp4?t=1641250627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE PARADE OF ONE HUNDRED DEMONS IS UPON YOU. CAN YOU SURVIVE?</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play through a wide collection of intense Microgames, each with its own different mechanics!<br></li><li>You have only a few seconds to beat each game! Better think fast!<br></li><li>So intense you’ll literally pee your pants!<br></li><li>But don’t worry! The whole game is played using only the arrow keys on your keyboard!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/fa834e7c4af3b93b9f195b9d6952100b.poster.avif?t=1641250627\" width=304 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/fa834e7c4af3b93b9f195b9d6952100b.webm?t=1641250627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/fa834e7c4af3b93b9f195b9d6952100b.mp4?t=1641250627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>\t\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787210/extras/4c7b2c81e625c27767492b7e370a42d9.poster.avif?t=1641250627\" width=304 height=172 ><source sr